  ('social-worker-moex-01137', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若某人出身頗具聲望的名校，我們就假定他一定學問很好、辦事能力也很強，這是犯了下列何種 錯誤？', '["選擇性觀察", "過度推論", "邏輯推理", "月暈效應"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b103121a72fe", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6d5b6600baad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0406", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01138', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '自從「不當管教」列入兒少保護個案評估的類型選項後，研究者由通報系統的資料分析發現這類 選項比例大幅增加，他想知道社工人員在勾選這項選項的想法和考量，下列那一種研究方法最能 找出答案？', '["焦點團體法", "介入實驗設計法", "記名問卷調查法", "行動研究法"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b103121a72fe", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6d5b6600baad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0406", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01139', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '現有證據指出，遭受同儕霸凌會損及身心健康。小明受到同學霸凌，因此我們推測他的心理健康 應該會受到影響，這是何種邏輯的應用？', '["歸納邏輯", "演繹邏輯", "矛盾邏輯", "實驗邏輯"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b103121a72fe", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6d5b6600baad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0406", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01140', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-110-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '科學知識建構的方法之一是在驗證事件因果關係，下列何者不是因果關係的條件？', '["因與果在時間上具先後關係", "因果關係要能排除干擾因素", "因與果的性質需抽象化", "因與果彼此之間有關聯"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:07+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b103121a72fe", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6d5b6600baad", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110030", "c": "105", "s": "0406", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
